        <p>Over the course of four days, moving through the Understand, Converge, and Diverge phases of the Sprint, the group gained consensus on a path forward. After all the discussing, brainstorming, sketching, writing, sharing, and voting we went through, it was really incredible to see a group that large come together on a singular idea.</p>

        <p>On Prototype day, the other designer and I collaborated on a prototype in Sketch that featured an onboarding flow that led the user to curated bundles of content that aligned with their interests. The idea would be that after answering a few questions at the beginning, they would receive a growth plan that featured curated content specific to their particular areas of desired growth. For example, if they said they wanted to be a better manager, they would get a bundle of articles, videos, and podcasts that would help grow their emotional intelligence.</p>

